      "markdown": "# 🕒 B5 — Present Tense: Regulars, Stem/Spelling Changes, Reflexives (B1)\n\n**Goal:** Learn how to conjugate **regular -ar/-er/-ir verbs** in the **present indicative**, including **stem/orthographic changes** and **reflexive verbs**.\n\nThis is the foundation tense for everyday conversation.\n\n---\n\n## 📌 Regular Endings\n\n| Person | -AR (*hablar*) | -ER (*comer*) | -IR (*vivir*) |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| yo | -o → *hablo* | -o → *como* | -o → *vivo* |\n| tú | -as → *hablas* | -es → *comes* | -es → *vives* |\n| él/ella/usted | -a → *habla* | -e → *come* | -e → *vive* |\n| nosotros/as | -amos → *hablamos* | -emos → *comemos* | -imos → *vivimos* |\n| vosotros/as | -áis → *habláis* | -éis → *coméis* | -ís → *vivís* |\n| ellos/ellas/ustedes | -an → *hablan* | -en → *comen* | -en → *viven* |\n\n> Ej.: *hablar → hablo, hablas, habla, hablamos, habláis, hablan*\n\n---\n\n## 🌱 Stem-Changing Verbs\n- **e → ie** (*pensar → pienso, piensas…*)  \n- **o → ue** (*dormir → duermo, duermes…*)  \n- **e → i** (*pedir → pido, pides…*)\n\n**⚠️ No change in nosotros / vosotros forms**\n\n---\n\n## ✍️ Orthographic Changes (yo form)\n- **-ger / -gir → -jo** (*proteger → protejo*)  \n- **-cer / -cir → -zco** (*conocer → conozco*)\n\n---\n\n## 💫 Reflexive Verbs\nUse **me/te/se/nos/os/se** + verb.  \nConjugate like normal and place the pronoun in front:\n\n> *Me levanto, te levantas, se levanta, nos levantamos, os levantáis, se levantan*\n\n---\n\n> 📝 Summary:\n> - Use present for habitual actions, facts, general truths  \n> - Remember stem/spelling changes  \n> - Reflexives need pronouns that agree with subject\n",
      "references": []
    }
  ],
